      </p>
      <p>
        For users in the EEA/UK, we rely on appropriate legal mechanisms for international data transfers, such as Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs) approved by the European Commission, where applicable.
      </p>
      <p>
        By using the Site, you consent to the transfer of your information to the United States and other countries for processing as described in this Privacy Policy.
      </p>
    </div>
